metadata.name: Leaf Your Life
metadata.description:
Captured in the timeless monochrome palette, this long exposure photograph reveals the transient dance of a leaf.
The motion blur embodies the essence of life's cycle, a fleeting moment frozen in time.
Reminding us of the leaf's graceful journey through seasons.
Leaving behind a trail of beauty and wisdom for eternity.

A7RMV | 135mm | F22 | ISO50 | 0.8s
9739 × 6826
